metadata.name: metadavid.eth - metadavid.eth and Friends Collection
metadata.description:
This is the profile picture of metadavid.eth.

David is an avid NFT collector and has also dabbled in creation. He is passionate about supporting emerging 1/1 artists in the NFT space. 

David's expertise is incubating emerging artists with hands-on support and growing their reach. He studied economics as an undergraduate, has an MBA, and is also completing a doctorate program where his research is centered around web3.

Always eager to connect and meet new people, do not hesitate to reach out to metadavid.eth!
